{"title":"Payments","slug":"payments","description":"Learn how you can manage payment settings","body":"# Payment process\r\n\r\nClickLion has simple payment process to make it easy for users to receive money from the platform. There are two payment processes.\r\n\r\n## Payment from a withdrawal\r\n\r\nIn ClickLion, you can withdraw funds from your wallet anytime you want. When we process the payment, we apply different payment method based on the amount you want to withdraw. If the amount is smaller than or equal to $10000, the payment will be sent to your Paypal account, otherwise we will wire the money directly to your bank account. When the wire transfer is being processed, corresponding transaction of the withdrawal will have status of `pending`.\r\n\r\n## Payment from monthly revenue\r\n\r\nClickLion users can [choose to be paid directly](#) when his or her revenue is delivered. In this case, if your revenue is smaller than ClickLion payment threshold ($100), the revenue will be still sent to your wallet, otherwise it will be processed as a withdrawal.\r\n\r\n> Transfer fee, if applicable, is covered by you.\r\n\r\n# Payment threshold\r\n\r\nTo avoid spammy withdrawals, ClickLion has a payment threshold of $100. You are allowed to withdraw only if your efficient payment amount is greater than or equal to $100.\r\n","_id":"wx6KFmmVne1WJnTv"}
{"title":"Account Management","slug":"account-management","description":"Learn how to view and edit account information","body":"# Account Setting\r\n\r\n## Change your password\r\n\r\nTo change your password, please follow these steps:\r\n\r\n1. [Sign in](http://prototype.clicklion.com/users/sign_in) to your ClickLion account.\r\n\r\n2. Hover over your avatar to reveal the dropdown menu and click **Edit Your Profile**.\r\n\r\n3. Choose ![](https://camo.githubusercontent.com/7119389da53464f8aa870f03c5bbf1a95cc1ee85/687474703a2f2f7075752e73682f6b7a704e722f376165366138366132352e706e67) from the left menu.\r\n\r\n4. Fill in the form to change your password.\r\n\r\n## Recover your password\r\n\r\nTo recover your password, please follow these steps:\r\n\r\n1. Click [here](http://prototype.clicklion.com/users/password/new) to go to the recovery form.\r\n\r\n2. Fill in your account email and submit the form.\r\n\r\n3. An email with instructions to recover your password will be sent to you within couple minutes. It might take a little longer in some unusual cases, but should not take more than 1 hour.\r\n\r\n4. Follow the instructions in the email to recover your password.\r\n\r\n## Update contact information\r\n\r\nTo update your contact information, please follow these steps:\r\n\r\n1. [Sign in](http://prototype.clicklion.com/users/sign_in) to your ClickLion account.\r\n\r\n2. Hover over your avatar to reveal the dropdown menu and click **Edit Your Profile**.\r\n\r\n3. Fill in the form and submit the changes.\r\n\r\n## Change payment information\r\n\r\nPayment information is very important please take all precautions to make sure you have entered all correct information. To change your payment information, please follow these steps:\r\n\r\n1. [Sign in](http://prototype.clicklion.com/users/sign_in) to your ClickLion account.\r\n\r\n2. Hover over your avatar to reveal the dropdown menu and click **Edit Your Profile**.\r\n\r\n3. Choose ![](https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c548ed1334ddee2fe9cf363c672118fa5a7c486c/687474703a2f2f7075752e73682f6b7a73304b2f383233646130636539392e706e67) from left menu.\r\n\r\n4. Fill in the form to change your payment information. The form contains following fields:\r\n\r\n  - **Payment Options**: This field specifies how ClickLion sends you payments. There are two options: `Pay Direct` and `Transfer to Wallet`. If you choose `Pay Direct`, ClickLion will issue payments via Paypal. Bank Transfer will be available to publisher who earn more than $10,000 a month. With `Transfer to Wallet` option ClickLion will send funds to your wallet, in which you can then use to pay for advertisement or withdraw anytime you chooses.\r\n\r\n  - **Paypal Email**: Your Paypal Account for ClickLion payments.\r\n\r\n  - **Bank Account**: Necessary information in order for us to wire payments to you.\r\n\r\n5. Submit the form to save your information.\r\n\r\n> Your information is secured, and we will not disclose any payment information to third parties.\r\n\r\n# Your Wallet\r\n\r\n## Add funds to your wallet\r\n\r\nTo purchase a campaign, you need to have funds in your wallet. To add funds to your wallet, please follow these steps:\r\n\r\n1. [Sign in](http://prototype.clicklion.com/users/sign_in) to your ClickLion account.\r\n\r\n2. Hover over your avatar to reveal the dropdown menu and click **Edit Your Profile**.\r\n\r\n3. Choose ![](https://camo.githubusercontent.com/86b97e9407e594d273ccfbfb164e4a7fcdae1424/687474703a2f2f7075752e73682f6b416d32572f663430613061393162622e706e67) from the left menu.\r\n\r\n4. Fill in the **Add Money to Your Balance** form.\r\n\r\n5. Click **Pay with Card** to proceed.\r\n\r\n> Every time you successfully add funds to your wallet, a [transaction](#) record will be created to represent your action. [Learn more](#) on transaction types.\r\n\r\n## Withdraw funds from your wallet\r\n\r\nTo withdraw fund from your wallet, please follow these step:\r\n\r\n1. [Sign in](http://prototype.clicklion.com/users/sign_in) to your ClickLion account.\r\n\r\n2. Hover over your avatar to reveal the dropdown menu and click **Edit Your Profile**.\r\n\r\n3. Choose ![](https://camo.githubusercontent.com/86b97e9407e594d273ccfbfb164e4a7fcdae1424/687474703a2f2f7075752e73682f6b416d32572f663430613061393162622e706e67) from the left menu.\r\n\r\n4. Fill in the **Withdraw** form.\r\n\r\n5. Click **Withdraw** to proceed.\r\n\r\n> Your minimum withdrawal amount is $100. In case the amount is smaller than $10,000, your withdrawn money will be transfered to your Paypal, otherwise it will be wire-transfered directly to your bank account.\r\n\r\n> Every time you successfully withdraw funds from your wallet, a [transaction](#) record classified as payout will be created to represent your action. [Learn more](#) on transaction types.\r\n\r\n## Pay for your campaign\r\n\r\nTO-DO","_id":"pz6Q33bqcfsQfFJT"}
